#####################################
Installation:
1. create a .env file in your project folder with the following (no brackets or ""):
APPID=<your app id>
TENANT=<your tenant name>
APIKEY=<your API key>
PORT=<PORT NUMBER, for example: 3000>

2. Open a commandline and go to your project folder. Run 'npm install' to
have all required packages installed.

#####################################
To run, simply type and execute in your commandline 'node session-app.js'
Open your browser go to http://localhost:<PORT NUMBER>


